      <hedline>
        <hl1>Corrections</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of June 22 article on Bayreuth Wagner Festival general director Wolfgang Wagner,</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>An article on June 22 about Wolfgang Wagner's actions as general director of the Bayreuth Festival, including the engagement of the director Christoph Marthaler, misstated the location of the Marthaler production of ''Pelléas et Mélisande'' seen by the writer. It was the Frankfurt Opera, not the Salzburg Festival.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>An article on June 22 about Wolfgang Wagner's actions as general director of the Bayreuth Festival, including the engagement of the director Christoph Marthaler, misstated the location of the Marthaler production of ''Pelléas et Mélisande'' seen by the writer. It was the Frankfurt Opera, not the Salzburg Festival.</p>
      </block>
